  "merger_description": "AtkinsR\u00e9alis Group Inc. through its wholly owned subsidiary AtkinsR\u00e9alis Engineering Pty Ltd (AtkinsR\u00e9alis), or otherwise through another wholly owned subsidiary (yet to be incorporated),\u00a0proposes to acquire 100% of the shares in WGA Group Holdings Pty Ltd (WGA) through a scheme of arrangement.\n\nAtkinsR\u00e9alis Group Inc. is a publicly traded, Canadian engineering and construction company with a global footprint. In Australia, AtkinsR\u00e9alis operates as a professional engineering and technical consultancy firm that provides engineering, design, advisory and delivery services to public and private customers across the transport, buildings and places, defence, energy and water sectors.\n\nWGA is a multi-disciplinary engineering and project management consultancy firm, which operates across Australia and New Zealand. It provides engineering, technical, advisory, delivery and project management services as stand-alone commissions or multi-disciplinary packages to both public and private clients across the following sectors: buildings urban development, defence and space, energy, ports and marine, resources, sports and recreation, transport and water.",
